2. Privacy Policy:

2.1 Introduction and scope

This Privacy Policy explains how SQOIN ("we", "us", or "our") collects, processes, and protects your personal information when you use Blockchain GPT, our websites, applications, and other online services (collectively referred to as the "Services"). By using our Services, you agree to the collection, processing, storage, and protection of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy.

2.2 Information collection and usage

We collect the following types of information to provide, improve, and maintain our Services:

2.2.1 Personal information

Personal information refers to information that can be used to identify you, either directly or indirectly. This may include your name, email address, contact information, billing information, device identifiers, IP address, and other information that we may collect during registration or while providing the Services.

2.2.2 Non-personal information

Non-personal information is data that cannot be used to identify you directly. We may collect non-personal information about your use of our Services, such as usage data, browsing history, search queries, and other anonymous data to help us understand user behavior and improve our Services.

2.3 Cookies and similar technologies

We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your user experience, remember your preferences, and analyze the performance of our Services. You can control or disable cookies through your browser settings. However, please note that certain features of our Services may not function properly if you disable cookies.

2.4 How information is used

